summary: Adds force to whirlwind sprint so it pushes away people and objects in the area when used, giving it a bit more realism.
descriptionHtml:
Adds force area of effect to all three words of Whirlwind Sprint. So whirlwind sprint pushes away people and objects in the area when used, giving it a bit more realism.

Works well with [url=http://www.skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/33578]Whirlwind Sprint less recharge time[/url].


How to install:
Extract zip file into TESV.exe directory or install using NMM.
author: Bluezone
